    "machine_start_gcode": "; ======= Start G-code for Lab4Makers CoreXY with Euclid Probe =======\nM190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single]      ; Wait for bed temp\nM109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer]          ; \nG28                                               ; Home all axes (Euclid handles deploy/dock)\nG1 Z5 F1800\nSKEW_PROFILE LOAD=my_skew_profile\nBED_MESH_PROFILE LOAD=default                     ; Load saved mesh profile (no adaptive mesh)\n\nM109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer]          ; Wait for nozzle to reach print temp\n\nG92 E0                                            ; Reset extruder\nG1 Z2.0 F3000                                     ; Lift nozzle to safe height\n\n; --- Purge / prime line ---\nG1 X20.1 Y20 Z0.28 F5000.0                        ; Move to purge start position\nG1 X20.1 Y250.0 Z0.28 F1500.0 E15                 ; Draw first purge line\nG1 X20.4 Y250.0 Z0.28 F5000.0                     ; Small move sideways\nG1 X20.4 Y20 Z0.28 F1500.0 E30                    ; Draw second purge line\nG1 Z0.40 F1200                                    ; Slightly lift for thick line\nG1 X22 Y20 F5000                                   ; Shift a bit away\nG1 X22 Y250 Z0.35 F1500.0 E40                     ; Fat purge line\nG92 E0                                            ; Reset extruder again\nG1 E-1.0000 F1800                                 ; Retract slightly\nG1 Z2.0 F3000                                     ; Lift nozzle\nG1 E0.0000 F1800                                  ; Re-prime for printing\n\n",
